quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,60,"Ko KaŇčko woni ∆īettitoowo on jemma, homo Anndi ko faggiti…óon √Īalawma. refti o Immintina on ontuma fii timmine lajal innaangal. refti ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon, refti o yeetitoo on kon ko ngollayno…óon."
  6,61,"Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo e dow jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďeen. Homo Nula e mo'on reenoo…ďe, haa si maayde nden arii go…ó…óo e mo'on, nulaa…ďe amen …ďen ∆īettita mo, kam…ďe …ďe mbelsintaako."
  6,62,"Refti …ďe ndutte ta Alla, gi…óo ma…ď…ďe goonga on. Faamee ko KaŇčko tan √Īaawoore nden woodani, ko KaŇčko …ďuri yaawude √Īaawoo…ďe."
  6,63,"Maaku : "Ko hommbo da…óndata on ni…ďe jeeri e maayo?" Ho…óon noddira mo yankinaare e gunndoo : "Si o da…óndii men e …óum …óoo, ma men jeye e yettoo…ďe …ďen"."
  6,64,"Maaku : "Ko Alla Da…óndata on e …óum, e kala ngo∆īo. Refti onon ho…óon cirka"."
  6,65,"Maaku : "Ko O kattan…óo nulugol lepte e dow mo'on, maa …óe iwra les koyde mon, maa o Jillindira on dente-dente, O Mee…óna yoga e mo'on lepte yoga". Ndaaru no men pirlitita Aayeeje …óen, mbelejo'o, …ďe paamat."
  6,66,"Yim…ďe maa …ďen njeddii ndee [Al Qur'aanaare], ko kayre le woni goonga kan. Maaku : "Mi wonaali e dow mon pawtii…óo"(.jogii…óo )"
  6,67,"Kala kumpital no mari √Īii…ďirde. Arma nganndoy."
  6,68,"Si a yi'ii …ďen jumpay…ďe e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …óuurno …ďe haa …ďe jumpa e yeewtere wo…ónde. Si seytaane yejjintinii ma, wata a joo…óoo …ďaawo annditugol ngol, e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen."